'''''Ewoks'' 9''' is the ninth issue of [[Star Wars: Ewoks (1985)|Marvel's ''Ewoks'']] series of comic books and was published under the [[Marvel Comics]] [[Star Comics]] imprint on [[June 3]], [[1986]] with a cover date of [[September]] 1986. This story is split into three chapters: "The Underwater Kingdom," "Danger in the Deep," and "The Ultimate Sacrifice."

